{
  "instrument": "rev2",
  "name": "Ghost Pluck",
  "description": "Springy resonant pluck with a haunting LFO vibrato that fades in via Envelope 3. The pluck body dies quickly; the reverb tail carries the wobble. High filter resonance provides the 'boing'. Vibrato blooms during the reverb decay.",
