    "Filter Env Amt: 127=zero, 254=max positive, 0=max negative",
    "Env 3 Amt: 127=zero, >127=positive. Used to fade in LFO 1 Amount.",
    "Env 3 Dest value 21 = LFO 1 Amount: vibrato fades in after attack",
